name: Rainbow Brite: Journey to Rainbow Land
overview:
With Rainbow Brite: Journey to Rainbow Land, enter a fun magical adventure dedicated to create a colourful world. Help Rainbow Brite and her pal Starlite in this classic RPG. Explore mazes and labyrinths, and face Murky and Murky the two evil ones trying to grey up the land. Defeat dozens of crawling, bouncing, and rolling…

Features:
– 6 levels of mazes and labyrinths
– Dozens of enemies
